author: ETA PRIME
description:
In this video, we’re taking the all-new GPD WIN 5 to the max!
This handheld may look small, but in docked mode, it transforms into a full-fledged gaming PC. We’re running the Ryzen MAX 385 (not the 395) with 32 GB RAM, tuned to a 65 W TDP, and the performance jump is insane — 1440p AAA gaming over 60 FPS on an integrated GPU!
We’ll compare 45 W vs 65 W benchmarks, run 3DMark, Geekbench 6, and test real games like Spider-Man 2, Forza Horizon 5, DOOM The Dark Ages, God of War Ragnarok, and Cyberpunk 2077.
You’ll also see how the twin-turbofan copper cooling system keeps temps under control even at 65 W, and why this handheld might just replace your desktop when docked. #etaprime #gpdwin5
